---
title: Chicken and Sage Sweet Potato Mash with Chili Maple Butter
description: A Southern staple turned on its head! We've swapped waffles for sweet potato mash in our take on a chicken dinner. A sweet drizzle of spiked maple syrup is the ultimate finish!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-and-sage-sweet-potato-mash-ce3bf60b.jpg
